snippet.title: Cover Yourself in Blood (2023) GAMEPLAY Trailer on Steam! #steam #cyib #coveryourselfinblood #blood
snippet.description:
Here is the STEAM trailer (GAMEPLAY) of "Cover Yourself in Blood" coming to the STEAM STORE soon!! This is so exciting!

Keep your eyes --- and flesh peeled, and be on the look out - the game is coming to STEAM!! Thank you to JORDANCUP, who added some skins in the game of NecroCaticGames characters!

CELEBRATION! We can Cover OURSELVES in Blood once again!!
